			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It's pretty much common knowledge that if you use your pet to pull. It's gonna get aggro based on it's level not yours. A good example of this would be our epic VS 60+ pets. Hunt in an area an try pet pulling with both. You'll see immediately that while pet pulling is a great resource, it is in most cases situational. The epic in most situations will gain social aggro almost immediately while our pop pets can successfully lure the mob solo. 
<br />

<br />
   If there are alot of nearby "potential adds" you may be better off pulling yourself with say an 8th level bolt or 5th level nuke. That way jobober can gain agggro almost immediatly.
<br />

<br />
Loscekiax Brokeitagain</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
