			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Initially when I read one of those post, topic about pulling single mob with the pet technique, I was assuming it meant the DB mobs.  But I guess what that turned out to be pulling greeines to light blue mobs.
<br />

<br />
For the Life of me, I can't single pull anything that is DB mobs with a pet, that isn't pullable single by me.  
<br />
i.g. If I can pull single mob, my pet is also able to do the same.
<br />

<br />
So rule of thumb, almost every one of mobs that are lightblue to greenies, you are able to pull singles without adds.  While pet can single pull them without aggro'ing adds (given that you pet is con blue to you).
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Archi</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
